WEBVTT

00:00:00.131 --> 00:00:04.716
This technological shift creates tension between business outcomes and human outcomes.

00:00:05.437 --> 00:00:11.625
You must navigate this through stability, the calculated balance of systemic disruption and cultural stability.

00:00:12.425 --> 00:00:16.490
You must provide stable anchors so your people feel safe enough to innovate rapidly.

00:00:17.331 --> 00:00:26.482
This requires radical employee centricity and empathy, applying cognitive empathy, emotional empathy, and empathic concern to eliminate low value work.
